channel.description:
Hey guys, I am putting together a remix EP for my album DISUNITY that just dropped 2 days ago, feel free to do whatever the hell you want when remixing these songs. I just want to hear your interpretations of these songs. The deadline for this EP will be next Saturday the 6th of June, good luck and have fun. https://soundcloud.com/user-156776670/sets/disunity
